<!-- This page is displayed when add_form_details view is called.
The javascript function addField() add four fields: Description, FieldType, RadioOptionvalues, Placeholder and validation.
The function is called when page is ready for displaying already created form.
Delete field is also present which deletes the already added 5 fields.--> 

{% extends "blank-page.html" %}
